{D66: Queen's Gambit Declined: Classical: Main Line (7 Rc1 c6 8 Bd3)} 1. d4 d5
2. c4 e6 3. Nf3 Nf6 4. Bg5 Be7 5. Nc3 Nbd7 6. e3 O-O 7. Rc1 c6 8. Bd3 c5 $146 (
8... Ne8 9. Bf4 (9. Bxe7 Qxe7 10. O-O f5 11. Qb3 Kh8 12. Ne5 Nef6 13. Nxd7 Qxd7
14. Qa3 Qf7 15. f3 Rg8 16. e4 f4 17. Qd6 g5 18. Rfe1 Nh5 19. exd5 g4 20. Qe5+
Nf6 21. Ne4 gxf3 22. Qxf6+ Qxf6 23. Nxf6 Rxg2+ {Antonsen,M (2380)-Flindt,T 
(2175) Esbjerg 2006 1-0}) 9... dxc4 (9... f5 10. h3 Nd6 11. Qb3 Kh8 12. g4 Qe8
13. cxd5 exd5 14. g5 Ne4 15. h4 Bd6 16. Ne2 Bxf4 17. Nxf4 Ng3 18. Rg1 Nh5 19.
Kd2 Nxf4 20. exf4 Qd8 21. Qb4 Nb6 22. Rce1 Nc4+ 23. Bxc4 dxc4 24. Re7 {Bareev,
E (2590)-Dovzik,J (2410) Dortmund 1990 1-0 (42)}) 10. Bxc4 Bd6 11. Bg3 Qc7 12.
Bd3 Nef6 13. Nd2 Bxg3 14. hxg3 e5 15. d5 h6 16. Bb1 Rd8 17. O-O Nb6 18. dxc6
Nc4 19. Nb5 Qxc6 20. Nxa7 Rxa7 21. Rxc4 Qd6 22. Rc1 Be6 23. Nc4 {Garcia
Gonzales,G (2535)-Radulov,I (2490) Buenos Aires 1978 0-1 (56)}) (8... h6 9.
Bxf6 Nxf6 10. c5 b6 11. Ne5 bxc5 12. Nxc6 Qd6 13. Nxe7+ Qxe7 14. dxc5 Qxc5 15.
O-O Qb4 16. Qe2 Rb8 17. b3 e5 18. e4 d4 19. Na4 Bd7 20. Nb2 Bb5 21. Nc4 Qe7 22.
f4 Bxc4 23. Rxc4 {Peist,J (2350)-Federau,J (2300) Germany 1988 0-1 (63)}) 9.
cxd5 exd5 10. O-O a6 {Consolidates b5} 11. Ne5 cxd4 (11... c4 $5 {deserves
consideration} 12. Be2 Nb6 $14) 12. exd4 $16 Nxe5 (12... Re8 13. Re1 $16) 13.
dxe5 $18 Nd7 $2 (13... Ng4 $142 14. Bf4 d4 $18) 14. Bxe7 Qxe7 15. Nxd5 Qxe5 16.
Re1 Qxb2 (16... Qg5 {no good, but what else?} 17. f4 Qh6 (17... Qxd5 $4 {
the knight is invulnerable} 18. Bxh7+ Kxh7 19. Qxd5 $18) 18. Ne7+ Kh8 19. Nxc8
Raxc8 20. Rxc8 Qb6+ 21. Kh1 Rxc8 $18) 17. Bxh7+ $1 {Mate attack} Kh8 (17...
Kxh7 18. Qh5+ {Mate attack}) 18. Qh5 (18. Rb1 $142 {and White has prevailed}
Qe5 19. Rxe5 Nxe5 $18) 18... Nf6 (18... Qd2 {there is nothing else anyway} 19.
f4 Nf6 20. Nxf6 Qd4+ 21. Kh1 Qxf4 22. Be4+ Qh6 $18) 19. Nxf6 (19. Nxf6 Qd2 20.
Bd3+ Qh6 21. Rc5 $18) 1-0

