Ba4 Nf6 5. O-O Nxe4 6. d4 b5 7. Bb3 d5 8. Nxe5 Nxe5 9. dxe5 Be6 10. Nd2 (10. c3
Bc5 11. Nd2 O-O 12. Nf3 f5 13. Nd4 Bxd4 14. Qxd4 c5 15. Qd1 f4 16. f3 Ng5 17.
a4 c4 18. Bc2 Bf5 19. b3 Bxc2 20. Qxc2 d4 21. axb5 d3 22. Qa2 axb5 23. Qxa8
Qxa8 24. Rxa8 Rxa8 {Ehlvest,J (2600)-Mamedyarov,S (2542) Kocaeli 2002 0-1 (33)}
) 10... Nxd2 11. Bxd2 c5 $146 (11... Bc5 12. Qf3 O-O 13. Be3 Bxe3 14. Qxe3 d4
15. Qe4 Bxb3 16. axb3 Qd7 17. b4 Rfd8 18. Ra3 Qe7 19. Rh3 h6 20. Rg3 Qxb4 21.
Qf4 Qe7 22. Qxh6 Qxe5 23. Qh4 Rd6 24. Rg5 Qf6 25. Qg3 Re8 26. Rg4 {Mrvova,A 
(2201)-Kantorik,M (2364) Tatranske Zruby 2009 0-1 (53)}) (11... Bc5 12. a3 $11)
12. c3 $14 Be7 {[%cal Yd5d4] Black intends d4} 13. Qf3 O-O 14. Rad1 d4 {
Black gains space} (14... Ra7 15. Qg3 Bh4 16. Qf4 $11) 15. Bxe6 (15. Be3 $5 $16
) 15... fxe6 $11 16. Qe4 (16. Qg4 Qd5 17. Bh6 Rf7 18. cxd4 cxd4 (18... Qxa2
$143 19. d5 Bf8 20. dxe6 $16) 19. Rxd4 Qxe5 $11) 16... d3 {Black has a new
passed pawn: d3} 17. Qc6 Qd5 18. Qxd5 exd5 {White has a new passed pawn: e5.
Black has new doubled pawns: d3+d5} 19. Be3 c4 {Black has a new protected
passed pawn: d3} 20. Bd4 {A sound move} (20. f4 a5 $11) 20... Kf7 $15 21. f4 {
White has a new protected passed pawn: e5} Ke6 22. g4 g6 23. Kg2 Rf7 24. Rf3
Raf8 25. Be3 b4 26. Kf2 bxc3 27. bxc3 Rb8 28. Kg3 h5 29. gxh5 gxh5 30. h4 $4 {
causes further problems for White.} (30. Rff1 $142 $17) 30... Kf5 31. Kh3 Rg7
32. Rg3 Rxg3+ 33. Kxg3 Rg8+ 34. Kh3 Rg4 35. Rb1 (35. Bd2 $19 {is one last hope}
) 35... Rxh4+ 36. Kg3 Rg4+ {[%cal Yh5h4] Black prepares h4} 37. Kf3 h4 38. Rb7
(38. Rh1 Rg3+ 39. Kf2 Kg4 $19) 38... Rg3+ 39. Kf2 Ke4 40. Bd2 (40. Ba7 Rg7 41.
Rb1 $19) 40... Bc5+ 41. Kf1 (41. Be3 {a fruitless try to alter the course of
the game} Bxe3+ 42. Ke1 Rg1#) 41... Rg1# 0-1

