material: Ng6xe5} 9. Bg2 Ncxe5 (9... O-O 10. Bg5 Qd7 11. O-O $14) 10. O-O Nxf3+
11. Bxf3 O-O {Black castles and improves king safety} 12. Rc1 c5 (12... Re8 13.
