Rxe5 19. Qd2 Bf5 (19... f6 20. Bd5+ Be6 21. Bxe6+ Rxe6 22. e3 $14) 20. e3 $16 {
White threatens to win material: e3xd4} Bg4 (20... Qf6 21. Bd5 $14) 21. exd4
Rxe1+ (21... Qxd4 $5 22. Qxd4 Rxe1+ 23. Rxe1 cxd4 $16) 22. Rxe1 $18 Qf6 (22...
cxd4 $142 23. h4 $1 {here's the full point} gxh4 $18) 23. Re5 h6 24. Rxc5 Re8
25. Re5 (25. Bxb7 $4 {a poisoned pawn} Re2 26. Qxe2 Bxe2 $19) 25... Re7 (25...
Rxe5 26. dxe5 Qxe5 27. Bxb7 $18) 26. Qe3 Be6 (26... Rxe5 {hoping against hope}
27. dxe5 Qf5 28. Bxb7 Qc2 $18) 27. d5 Kf8 (27... b6 {doesn't change the
outcome of the game} 28. b4 $18) 28. dxe6 Rxe6 (28... fxe6 {is not much help}
29. Bh3 $18) 29. Rxe6 Qxe6 (29... fxe6 {is not the saving move} 30. Qc5+ Kf7
