11. f3 {Controls e4+g4} (11. Nf3 $5 $11) 11... c5 $15 12. O-O-O c4 {Black
threatens to win material: c4xd3} 13. Be2 cxb3 14. axb3 Nb6 15. e4 {[%cal
Yd4d5] White prepares the advance d5} a5 16. d5 {This push gains space} (16.
Nb5 $5 {is worth consideration} Qd8 17. d5 $15) 16... Bd7 $17 {[%cal Ya5a4]
Black prepares the advance a4} 17. Ng4 $2 (17. e5 $142 $5 dxe5 18. d6 exd6 19.
