) 33. Qd4 Qa5 34. Bf3 (34. Qe3 Rc4 $17) 34... Bb5 35. Rb3 Rc4 36. Rxb5 $4 {
strolling merrily down the path to disaster} (36. Qd3 Rc5 37. Qd2 Qa1+ 38. Rb1
