exf6+ gxf6 41. Kxg3 Kd6 $19) 37... Kd6 38. Na5 (38. Bxa7 Kxc6 39. Kf2 Be6 $19)
38... Be6 39. Bxa7 Kc7 (39... Nc1 $142 $19 {and Black has reached his goal})
40. Bc5 $17 b3 41. Nxb3 Bxb3 {Black wins a piece} 42. Bf8 g6 43. Bg7 (43. Bxh6
Kxc6 44. Bg7 Nb4 $17) 43... f5 (43... Nb4 $142 $19 {Black would have gained
the upper hand}) 44. Bxe5+ $15 Kxc6 45. exf5 gxf5 46. Kf2 Kd5 {Black threatens
to win material: Kd5xe5} (46... Nb4 47. Kg3 $17) 47. Bg7 h5 48. Kg3 Ke6 49. Kf4
$2 (49. Kh4 $142 $5 $11 {is an interesting alternative}) 49... Kf7 $17 50. Bd4
(50. Be5 Kg6 $17) 50... Kg6 51. g4 1/2-1/2

