Ned4 Nb4 17. Bb1 Rac8 18. Nxe6 Rxc1 19. Qxc1 fxe6 20. a3 Nc6 21. Bxe4 dxe4 22.
Nd2 Rd3 {Smyslov,V (2520)-Yudasin,L (2605) Biel 1993 1/2-1/2}) 8... a5 $146 {
Black has a very active position} (8... O-O 9. Be2 a6 10. b4 d4 11. exd4 Bxd4
12. Nxd4 Nxd4 13. O-O Bf5 14. Bg5 Nxe2+ 15. Nxe2 Qxd1 16. Rfxd1 Ne4 17. Be3
