10. Ne2 Ne4 11. b4 Ba7 12. Bb2 Qe7 13. Qb3 a5 14. b5 a4 15. Qc2 Na5 16. Ned4
Bd7 17. Qxa4 Nc4 18. Qb3 Bc5 19. Bxc4 dxc4 20. Qxc4 Rfc8 21. O-O Bxa3 22. Bxa3
Rxa3 23. Qd5 {Guseva,M (2195)-Burtasova,A (2160) Peniscola 2002 1-0 (34)}) 9.
Bd3 O-O 10. O-O Re8 11. Qc2 (11. h3 Ne5 $11) 11... Bf8 (11... Bg4 $5 $15) 12.
Rd1 Bg4 {Black has an active position} 13. Be2 Rc8 14. Qb3 {[%cal Rb3d5,Rc3d5,
Rd1d5,Gd8d5,Gf6d5] Increasing the pressure on the isolated pawn on d5. White
threatens to win material: Qb3xb7} Qe7 15. Nxd5 Nxd5 16. Qxd5 Rcd8 {Black
threatens to win material: Rd8xd5} (16... Ne5 17. Qxa5 Bxf3 18. Bxf3 Nxf3+ 19.
gxf3 $11) 17. Qb3 (17. Qb5 Rxd1+ 18. Bxd1 Qd8 $14) 17... Ne5 18. Bd2 Bxf3 19.
Bxf3 Rd3 (19... Nxf3+ $142 20. gxf3 Qf6 $11) 20. Qxb7 $4 {weakening the
position} (20. Bc3 $142 Nxf3+ 21. gxf3 Rxe3 22. fxe3 Qxe3+ 23. Kg2 Qe2+ 24. Kg3
$11) 20... Qxb7 $19 21. Bxb7 Red8 22. f4 Ng6 (22... Nc4 23. Ba6 Rxd2 24. Rxd2
