b4 axb4 25. axb4 Bxb4 $19) 24... Rb8 25. Be4 (25. Ba6 {doesn't change the
outcome of the game} Rbxb2 26. Rxb2 Rxb2 $19) 25... Rbxb2 26. Ra1 (26. Rxb2 {
doesn't get the cat off the tree} Rxb2 27. Rc1 Bxa3 28. Rc8+ Nf8 $19) 26... Bc5
27. h3 (27. Kh1 {cannot change what is in store for White} Re2 $19) 27... Nxf4
(27... f5 {and Black can already relax} 28. Bf3 Nh4 29. Rac1 Nxg2 30. Bxg2
Rxg2+ 31. Kh1 Rh2+ 32. Kg1 Bxa3 33. Rc8+ Kf7 34. Rc7+ Kg6 35. Rb1 $19) 28. Rac1
