16. Nxc8 Raxc8 17. Qa4 a6 18. Rfe1 Na5 19. Rad1 Rcd8 {Bogosavljevic,B (2302)
-Ravic,N (2151) Vrnjacka Banja 2006 1/2-1/2 (32)}) 5... h6 {Covers g5} 6. Nf3
Nbd7 7. Nbd2 c6 {Prevents intrusion on b5} 8. c3 {Covers b4} O-O 9. O-O a6 {
Controls b5} 10. Re1 {Black's piece can't move: c8} Re8 11. e4 dxe4 12. Nxe4 b5
13. Nd6 Bxd6 14. Bxd6 Nb6 15. Bh2 (15. Ba3 Bb7 $16) 15... Bb7 16. Ne5 Nbd7 (
