Nb6 18. Qc2 $16) 18. Qc2 (18. b4 a5 $16) 18... Rad8 (18... c5 19. Ne5 $11) 19.
Ne5 (19. b4 a5 $16) 19... Nf8 (19... c5 $142 $5 $14 {must definitely be
considered}) 20. b4 Nd5 21. Rac1 f6 22. Ng6 (22. Nf3 Ra8 $16) 22... Bc8 (22...
Nxg6 23. Bxg6 Re7 24. Bg3 $16) 23. Nxf8 (23. Nf4 a5 24. a3 Re7 $16) 23... Rxf8
24. Qe2 Qb7 25. Qh5 Qe7 26. Qg6 f5 27. g4 (27. Be5 $5 $16) 27... Rf6 $11 {
Black threatens to win material: Rf6xg6} 28. Qh5 {Black king safety improved}
Rdf8 (28... fxg4 $142 $5 {has some apparent merit} 29. Qxg4 e5 $11) 29. gxf5
$16 Rxf5 $2 (29... Qd8 $142 $16) 30. Bxf5 $18 Rxf5 31. Qd1 $4 {White loses the
upper hand} (31. Qxf5 $142 $1 exf5 32. Rxe7 Nxe7 33. Bd6 $18) 31... Qf7 (31...
Qh4 32. Bg3 Qxh3 33. Re5 $11) 32. Re2 (32. Bg3 $142 $16) 32... Rg5+ $15 33. Kf1
$4 (33. Bg3 $142 {was a good chance to save the game} Nf4 34. h4 Nxe2+ 35. Qxe2
$11) 33... Qf3 $19 34. Ke1 (34. Re5 {doesn't do any good} Qh1+ (34... Qxh3+
