Ka8 79. Bd5#) 73... Kb8 74. Be4 Ka7 (74... Kc7 {does not improve anything} 75.
a7 Kd6 76. a8=Q Ke5 77. a6 Kf4 78. a7 Kg4 79. Qg8+ Kf4 80. a8=Q Ke3 81. Qg3+
