Arencibia Rodriguez,W (2420)-Alzate,D (2365) Medellin 1987 1-0 (36)}) (4...
cxd4 5. cxd4 Nc6 6. Nf3 Nb4 7. O-O (7. Nc3 Nxd3+ 8. Qxd3 d6 9. O-O Be7 10. d5
e5 11. h3 O-O 12. Be3 Nh5 13. Qe2 g6 14. Rac1 Bd7 15. b4 Ng7 16. Nd2 f5 17.
exf5 Nxf5 18. Nde4 Nxe3 19. fxe3 Qb6 20. a3 Kg7 21. Rxf8 Rxf8 {Krapivin,A 
